comments: Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in a legal picking position in LaVine's (CHI) path.
While the foul call is correct the contact from Carter Jr. (CHI) occurs after Lillard (POR) has gathered the ball and continuation should be granted.
Nurkic (POR) legally firms up in LaVine's (CHI) path and does not deliver any contact during the pick.
LaVine (CHI) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) body during his jump shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Jones Jr.'s (POR) path and does not deliver any contact.
Nurkic (POR) makes marginal contact with Young (CHI) during the drive.

After Nurkic (POR) initiates marginal contact with Young (CHI), Young slightly extends his off-arm. The contact is marginal and Nurkic is able to defend the shot attempt at the basket. The reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Nurkic (POR) maintains a legal vertical position as he defends Young's (CHI) driving shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (CHI) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Covington (POR) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Jones Jr. (POR) engages and disengages with Porter Jr. (CHI) during the rebound.
Covington (POR) makes contact with Porter Jr.'s (CHI) arm.
Covington (POR) establishes himself in a legal defensive position outside of the RA and absorbs the contact delivered by Young (CHI) during the play at the basket.
Temple (CHI) makes contact with Lillard (POR) that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Jones Jr. (POR) makes incidental foot to foot contact with LaVine (CHI).
Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in a legal defensive position and absorbs the contact from LaVine (CHI) on the gather.
Young (CHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Jones Jr.'s (POR) path.
Temple (CHI) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR) as Lillard abruptly stops in Temple's path.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on White (CHI).
White (CHI) legally defends Anthony's (POR) jump shot attempt.
